    dc:description "FIGURES 21 – 30. Midoria curvidentata sp. nov. 21, habitus, dorsal view; 22, habitus, lateral view; 23, forewing; 24, face; 25, subgenital plate, ventral view; 26, magnified aedeagus, ventral view; 27, pygofer, lateral view; 28, male 8 th sternite, ventral view; 29, aedeagus, style and connective, lateral view; 30, aedeagus and connective, ventral view. Scale bars = 1.0 mm (Figs. 21 - 24); 0.4 mm (Figs. 25,27 - 30); 0.1 mm (Figs. 26)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/832734/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

